!-----------------------------------------------------------------------
!     Example to generate spherical harmonics index data files
!-----------------------------------------------------------------------
!
 Here is the files to generate spherical harmonics index data file
for simulations with 6 MPI processes.
 In this example, Chebyshev points are used for the radial spacing
including inner core and external of the core.
This example consists of the following files and directories

control_sph_shell:   control file for data transform
sph_lm31r48c_4_ic:   Directory for spherical harmonics index table

Run index generation program in both directory for index tables
[with_inner_core]$ [CALYPSO_DIR]/bin/utilities/gen_sph_grids
